  /ySP ED /xSP ED /y1 ED /x1 ED 
  /dx xSP x1 sub 3 div def 
  /dy ySP y1 sub 3 div def 
  newpath x1 y1 moveto xSP y1 lineto xSP ySP lineto 
                       x1 ySP lineto closepath clip 
  currentpoint
  newpath moveto
